# Docs and articles (private only)
docs/
Articles/
simulator/data/

# Binary artifacts — audit fix 2026-05-08 (P0 cross-project synthesis #4):
# .docx/.pdf/.xlsx blob the repo with versioned binaries that don't diff.
# Source-of-truth markdown lives in Materials/<topic>/*.md (track those only).
Materials/**/*.docx
Materials/**/*.pdf
Materials/**/*.xlsx
Materials/**/*.pptx
*.docx
*.xlsx
*.pptx
# .pdf allowed only in Articles/ (already gitignored above) — block elsewhere:
*.pdf
!Articles/*.pdf
